{
  "screen_id": "market-trade",
  "route": "/market/trade",
  "title": "取引",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "c8(ui-asset-catalog.md 【最優先1】)再構築版・UI磨き第2弾(受領10)で追改修。MKT-03/23/25/20。目的起点=3タブ[この出品/取引|買う|出品する]。「この出品/取引」が既定(listing_id 付きで開いた時に即詳細が見える・market.spec.ts 互換)。stage(公開1→非公開ボード2)は内側の stage-tabs が data.state.stage に自動追従(手動タップも可・タブは隠さない=stage 出し分けは tabs のまま)。4段stepper は current_from/current_map(BadgeNode の derive_from+labels 流用)で MARKET_EDGES の実 state 群を4visual stepへ縮退。振込は round-16 決済裁定どおり銀行振込P2P・GMO非関与 — pay_declare(買い手)/pay_confirm(出品者)/ship(出品者)/receive(買い手)の4トグルは磨き第2弾#1で `when`(役割別出し分けプリミティブ・{{viewer.actor_id}} vs {{data.state.seller_id}}/matched_with)を付与し、受領10「買い手/売り手のみ表示」を解消(両方常時表示だった旧UIから変更)。出品写真は磨き第2弾#2でschemas/events/mkt-listing-photo.schema.json(新イベント型・mkt-listing 本体は無変更)+POST /market/listings/{id}/photo で追加、出品フォームに photo field・「買う」タブは table から image-grid へ差し替え(カードタップ=詳細・受領10「画像を押せば詳細が出る」)。bids-table の入札者列・非公開board の from は磨き第2弾#5で actor 表示プリミティブ(表示名 or 短縮ハッシュ)化。相手選別なしdispute起票の respondent_id 自動判定(出品者/落札者どちらが起票者かの一般判定)は本波未対応(候補提示+手動確認のまま・別要件)。個体仕様table/送料見積りは対象外(schemas/events/mkt-listing.schema.json に individual_ids フィールドが無く実データ不在のため — 誇張ゼロ、飾りで埋めない)。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            { "id": "title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text": "取引", "level": 1 } },
            {
              "id": "market-tabs",
              "type": "tabs",
              "props": {
                "tabs": [
                  { "id": "detail", "label": "この出品/取引" },
                  { "id": "browse", "label": "買う" },
                  { "id": "create", "label": "出品する" }
                ],
                "default_tab": "detail"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "detail",
                  "type": "card",
                  "props": {
                    "tab_id": "detail",
                    "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}",
                    "bind_text": "{{listing.title}} / {{listing.price}} 円",
                    "meta": "{{data.detail.listing.description}}",
                    "badges": [ { "text": "成立方式 {{data.detail.listing.accept_mode}}" } ],
                    "empty_text": "listing_id を指定してください(「買う」タブから選ぶか、下の「出品する」タブから作成できます)。"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "state",
                  "type": "card",
                  "props": {
                    "tab_id": "detail",
                    "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/state",
                    "bind_text": "状態 {{state}}（ステージ {{stage}}）"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "stage-stepper",
                  "type": "stepper",
                  "props": {
                    "tab_id": "detail",
                    "steps": [
                      { "id": 0, "label": "出品" },
                      { "id": 1, "label": "成立・振込" },
                      { "id": 2, "label": "発送・受取" },
                      { "id": 3, "label": "完了" }
                    ],
                    "current_from": "{{data.state.state}}",
                    "current_map": {
                      "unlisted": 0, "listed_fixed": 0, "listed_auction": 0, "listed_lottery": 0,
                      "listed_platinum": 0, "offer_pending": 0, "cancelled": 0, "delisted": 0,
                      "matched": 1,
                      "shipped": 2, "received": 2, "rated": 2,
                      "sold": 3
                    }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "stage-tabs",
                  "type": "tabs",
                  "props": {
                    "tab_id": "detail",
                    "tabs": [
                      { "id": "1", "label": "公開情報(価格・入札)" },
                      { "id": "2", "label": "取引ボード(成立後)" }
                    ],
                    "default_tab": "{{data.state.stage}}"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "id": "price",
                      "type": "kpi-tile",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "1",
                        "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/price-recommendation",
                        "value": "{{data.price.anchor}} 円",
                        "label": "推奨価格(過去成約から都度算出・embedding既定OFF)",
                        "trend": "{{data.price.method}}"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "bids-table",
                      "type": "table",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "1",
                        "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/state",
                        "bind_items": "data.bids-table.bids",
                        "columns": [
                          { "key": "bidder", "label": "入札者", "cell": "actor" },
                          { "key": "amount", "label": "金額(円)" },
                          { "key": "at", "label": "日時", "cell": "date" }
                        ],
                        "empty_text": "入札はまだありません。"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-publish",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "1",
                        "label": "この出品を公開する(未出品→公開・即決既定)",
                        "variant": "primary",
                        "static": { "kind": "list_fixed", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-match",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "1",
                        "label": "この出品に申込む(即決=申込確定で成立)",
                        "variant": "primary",
                        "static": { "kind": "match", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "payment",
                      "type": "card",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/state",
                        "bind_text": "支払い方法 {{payment.method}}・振込済み申告 {{payment.declared_at}}・入金確認 {{payment.confirmed_at}}(round-16決済裁定: 銀行振込P2P・IHL非関与)"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "payment-notice",
                      "type": "text",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "text": "代金のやり取りは銀行振込のみをご利用ください。PayPay送金等の個人間送金アプリはご利用いただけません(利用規約で明示禁止)。"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "board",
                      "type": "list",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/board",
                        "bind_items": "data.board.offers",
                        "item_actor_field": "from",
                        "item_text": "{{kind}} {{amount}}",
                        "empty_text": "非公開ボードはまだありません(成立後・当事者2人のみ開きます)。"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-pay-declare",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "label": "振込済みを申告する(買い手)",
                        "variant": "primary",
                        "static": { "kind": "pay_declare", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" },
                        "when": { "eq": ["{{viewer.actor_id}}", "{{data.state.matched_with}}"] }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-pay-confirm",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "label": "入金を確認した(出品者)",
                        "variant": "primary",
                        "static": { "kind": "pay_confirm", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" },
                        "when": { "eq": ["{{viewer.actor_id}}", "{{data.state.seller_id}}"] }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-ship",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "label": "発送した(出品者)",
                        "variant": "secondary",
                        "static": { "kind": "ship", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" },
                        "when": { "eq": ["{{viewer.actor_id}}", "{{data.state.seller_id}}"] }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-receive",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "label": "受け取りました(検品OK・買い手)",
                        "variant": "primary",
                        "static": { "kind": "receive", "listing_id": "{{params.listing_id}}" },
                        "when": { "eq": ["{{viewer.actor_id}}", "{{data.state.matched_with}}"] }
                      },
                      "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{params.listing_id}}/transition" }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "dispute-hint",
                      "type": "text",
                      "props": {
                        "tab_id": "2",
                        "text": "相手方候補(出品者/落札者): {{data.state.seller_id}} / {{data.state.matched_with}}",
                        "muted": true
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "btn-dispute",
                      "type": "button",
                      "props": { "tab_id": "2", "label": "相違・死着 → dispute相談室へ", "variant": "secondary" },
                      "action": {
                        "kind": "navigate",
                        "to": "dispute?category=market&subject_type=listing&subject_id={{params.listing_id}}&respondent_id={{data.state.seller_id}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "listings-grid",
                  "type": "image-grid",
                  "props": {
                    "tab_id": "browse",
                    "source_path": "/api/v1/market/listings",
                    "bind_items": "data.listings-grid.listings",
                    "item_image": "/api/v1/market/listings/{{listing_id}}/photo/{{cover_photo_id}}",
                    "item_alt": "{{title}}",
                    "item_label": "{{title}} / {{price}} 円",
                    "item_badge": "{{accept_mode}}",
                    "item_href": "/s/market-trade?listing_id={{listing_id}}",
                    "empty_text": "出品はまだありません。"
                  }
                },
            {
              "id": "create-hint",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "tab_id": "create",
                "text": "出品は下書き(未出品)として作成されます。作成後は自動でこの画面に戻るので「この出品/取引」タブから公開してください。",
                "muted": true
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "create-listing-form",
              "type": "form",
              "props": { "tab_id": "create" },
              "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/market/listings" },
              "children": [
                { "id": "new-title", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "text", "name": "title", "label": "出品タイトル", "required": true } },
                { "id": "new-photo", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "photo", "name": "photo", "label": "個体写真(任意・「買う」タブの一覧に表示されます)" } },
                { "id": "new-description", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "textarea", "name": "description", "label": "説明(任意)" } },
                { "id": "new-price", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "number", "name": "price", "label": "希望価格(円・任意)" } },
                {
                  "id": "new-accept-mode",
                  "type": "field",
                  "props": {
                    "variant": "select",
                    "name": "accept_mode",
                    "label": "成立方式",
                    "placeholder": "成立方式を選ぶ",
                    "options": [
                      { "value": "instant", "label": "即決(既定・申込確定=成立)" },
                      { "value": "consent", "label": "承諾制(応相談・24h以内に承諾)" }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                { "id": "new-submit", "type": "button", "props": { "type": "submit", "label": "下書きを作成する", "variant": "primary" } }
              ]
            }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [
    { "from": "btn-publish", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "公開後に再読込" },
    { "from": "btn-match", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "申込(成立)後に再読込" },
    { "from": "btn-pay-declare", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "振込申告後に再読込" },
    { "from": "btn-pay-confirm", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "入金確認後に再読込" },
    { "from": "btn-ship", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "発送後に再読込" },
    { "from": "btn-receive", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "受取確定後に再読込" },
    { "from": "create-listing-form", "to_screen_id": "market-trade", "label": "下書き作成後に再読込" }
  ]
}
